    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo ka warretu es us aug-\nfchu aiseet pee fawa Tehwa/ ja\ntas Puifis ar man ne buhtu/ ka\nes tohs Gird-Ehftus ne redsu/kas\nmannam Tehwam pee-eetit."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ad ne warreja Jahseps\nfaturretees preekfch wiſ-\nfeim/ kas pee winna\nstahweja/ un fanze: iſweddeet\nikkatru Wihru no mannim ahra/\nun ne weens stahweja pee ta/ kad\nJahseps few pasihstamu darrijahs\nfaweem Brahteem."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſsch pazehle fatwu\nBalsi randadamis/ ta/ ka tee E-\ngipteri to dsirdeja / un Waraus\nSaime to dsirdeja."
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jahseps fazzija us fa-\nweem Brahteem: Es efimu Jah-\nseps/ irrag mans Tehios wehl\ndsihws? un winna Brahti ne\nwarreja tain athildeht/ jo tee\npreekfch winna Waiga pahrbih-\njajahs."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jahseps fazzija us fa-\nweem Brahteem: Pee-eite jelle\nflaht pee man/ un tee peegahje/\ntad fazzija wiſsch: Es efimu Jah-\nseps juhsfu Brahtis/ ko juhs effat\nahrdeuutchi us Egiptes-Seint."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un nu/ne behdajeet\nne israngajt batligt/ ka ju-\nschurp eſtat pahr dewufe-\nDeews irr mann juhfu P-\nschurp fuhtijis/ juhtu D-\nUsturreſchanas pehz."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo Schis irr tas oht-\nda-Gads pahr wiffu Sen-\nwehl buhs peezi Gaddi-\nbuhs Arſchana / ned-\nſchana."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Deews irr man-\nPreefscha fuhtijis/ ka wi-\npahri paturretu wirs S-\nun juhs dsihwus glahbt-\nweenu leelu Iſpestischan-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un nu/ juhs ne eff-\ntchurp fuhtijufchi / bet-\nkas mann Waraim par-\nlizzis irr/ un par Kung-\nwinna Namna/ un par-\ntaju wiffas Egiptes-Sen-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Steidseetees / un\naugchu pee mannim Teh-\nfakkajt us to: Ta fatt-\nDehis Jahseps: Deews ir-\neezeblis par Kungu wiffa-\ntes Semmes / nahz sch-\nman/ ne kawejees."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tew buhs dsihwoh-\nGosena Semmes/ un bu-\nwu pee man/ tu/ un tawi-\nun tawo Dehlu Dehli / u-\nfihki Lohpi / un tawi We-\nun wiff/ kas tew peederr."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es tewtur ustur-\njo tur irr wehl peezi Badda-\ndi/ ka tu jafchn Truhkum-\nnihkti/ tu/ un taws Nam-\nwiff/ kas tew peederr."
    }
  ],
